Package model

Class Toys

java.lang.Object
model.Toys
Direct Known Subclasses:
Animals, BoardGames, Figures, Puzzles
public abstract class Toys extends Object
This abstract class represents a toy object. It contains the serial number, name, brand, price, availability count, appropriate age range, and type of toy. It also will encapsulate the attributes into one string then properly format it.
Version:
1.0

      Constructor for the Toys class

      serialNumber - serial number of the toy (unique, 10 digits)
      name - name of the toy
      brand - brand of the toy
      price - price of the toy
      availabityCount - how many toys are available in inventory
      ageAppropriate - appropriate age range for the toy
      toyType - type of toy (Puzzle, Board Game, Figure, or Animal)
